      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   SYSIN GET MOVE
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3000-SYSDATA-MOVE-RTN.

           INITIALIZE    WK-HOST-IN

      *    그룹회사구분코드
           MOVE  WK-SYSIN-GROUP-CD
             TO  WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *    기준년월
           MOVE  WK-SYSIN-BASE-YMD(1:6)
             TO  WK-H-I-BASE-YM
      *    기준일
           MOVE  WK-SYSIN-BASE-YMD(7:2)
             TO  WK-H-I-BASE-DD
      *    기준년월일
           MOVE  WK-SYSIN-BASE-YMD
             TO  WK-H-I-BASE-YMD
      *    전영업년월일
           MOVE  WK-SYSIN-BEFORE-YMD
             TO  WK-H-I-BEFORE-YMD

      *    전년도말월 = 기준년 - 1년 + '12'
           MOVE  WK-SYSIN-BASE-YMD(1:4)
             TO  WK-BASE-YEAR

           COMPUTE WK-BEFORE-YEAR = WK-BASE-YEAR - 1

           MOVE  WK-BEFORE-YEAR
             TO  WK-H-I-BEFORE-YM(1:4)

           MOVE '12'
             TO WK-H-I-BEFORE-YM(5:2)

                             .
       S3000-SYSDATA-MOVE-EXT.
           EXIT.
