      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3300-KJL0069-INSERT-RTN.

           INITIALIZE    TKJL0069-KEY
                         TRJL0069-REC


      *    그룹회사코드
           MOVE  WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  RJL0069-GROUP-CO-CD

      *    기준년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-I-BASE-YMD
             TO  RJL0069-BASE-YMD

      *    대분류업종코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-LAG-CLSFI-BZTYP-CD
             TO  RJL0069-LAG-CLSFI-BZTYP-CD

      *   지역구분
           MOVE  WK-H-O-AREA-DSTCD
             TO  RJL0069-AREA-DSTCD


           EVALUATE  WK-GUBUN
               WHEN  CO-CHA-1
