      *              지역별익스포져금액
                     MOVE  WK-H-O-SUB-CLAM
                       TO  RJL0069-AREA-PER-EXPSR-AMT

               WHEN  CO-CHA-2
      *              전년도말익스포져금액
                     MOVE  WK-H-O-SUB-CLAM
                       TO  RJL0069-PYY-X-END-EXPSR-AMT

               WHEN  CO-CHA-3
      *              증가익스포져금액
                     MOVE  WK-H-O-SUB-CLAM
                       TO  RJL0069-INCRSE-EXPSR-AMT

               WHEN  CO-CHA-4
      *              지역별SUB한도
                     MOVE  WK-H-O-SUB-CLAM
                       TO  RJL0069-AREA-PER-SUB-CLAM
           END-EVALUATE

      *    한도초과년월일
           MOVE  SPACES
             TO  RJL0069-LIMT-EXCS-YMD

      *    예외적용년월일
           MOVE  SPACES
             TO  RJL0069-ECEPT-APLY-YMD


           #DYDBIO  INSERT-CMD-Y TKJL0069-PK TRJL0069-REC

           EVALUATE  TRUE
               WHEN  COND-DBIO-OK
                     ADD   CO-NUM-1    TO  WK-AC-INT-CNT
               WHEN  COND-DBIO-DUPM
                     PERFORM S3310-KJL0069-UPDATE-RTN
                        THRU S3310-KJL0069-UPDATE-EXT

               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE 'KJL0069'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                     MOVE 'INSERT'     TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                     MOVE  DBIO-SQLCODE
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
