                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                     #ERROR  CO-EBM05001 CO-UBM05001 DBIO-STAT
                     #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-EVALUATE


                               .
       S3300-KJL0069-INSERT-EXT.
           EXIT.
